hi.

i was working on this a while ago.

it was meant to be an expansive collab with many contributors, all making speedrun map type levels which were to be sandwhiched together such that you couldn't keep speed, leading to individual routing per level.

except only me pcpie and dream made levels, so here is the result after about 1/2 a year of waiting to see if anyone else ever made a level.

enjoy.

gl;hf

p.s.: i'm lazy so didn't optimize anyones stages beyond what they had done.

lvl1: dream
lvl2: george
lvl3: pcpie
